				<wikidot:authorName>Kykywox</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2784501</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, it would appear that, 5 years later, <a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" target="_blank">TwistedGears</a> has graced us with <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2284" target="_blank">Mr.Lie's SCP</a>! :D</p> <p>I love slowly piecing all of these together. Maybe when I'm done reading them (in 5 trillion years) I'm finally gonna be able to finish reading <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3301" target="_blank">SCP-3301</a> without opening new tangents!</p> <p>Love the whole exasperation of Mr. Lie's condition.<br /> +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
